Scientific Agent Tools Upstream Notice

This plugin incorporates and adapts maintainer-facing authoring and context
maintenance patterns from:
- https://github.com/ed3dai/ed3d-plugins
- https://github.com/ed3dai/ed3d-plugins/tree/main/plugins/ed3d-extending-claude

The initial draft of this plugin directory was copied from a modified ed3d
plan and then refit for this repository's current contracts.

Repo-specific adaptations include:
- plugin-scoped source-of-truth paths under `plugins/`
- `CODEX_HOME` installation layout for Codex
- synchronized runtime-compatibility blocks
- AGENTS-first context guidance with optional CLAUDE companion files
- local skill namespaces such as `scientific-plan-execute:*` and
  `scientific-agent-tools:*`
